author: Doug Stanglin
description: The 52-year-old Democratic politician, who is separated from Hillary Clinton aide Huma Abedin, could face a prison term and must register as a sex offender.
title: Anthony Weiner pleads guilty to sexting with minor; Huma Abedin files for divorce

author: Ben Kew
description: The wife of disgraced former New York congressman Anthony Weiner, Huma Abedin, has finally filed for divorce on the same day he plead guilty to charges of sexting a minor.
title: Report: Huma Abedin Finally Files for Divorce from Anthony Weiner - Breitbart

author: Benjamin Weiser and William K. Rashbaum
description: The ex-congressman, whose wife, Huma Abedin, was a top aide to Hillary Clinton, admitted to sending sexually explicit images to a girl he knew was 15.
title: Anthony Weiner Pleads Guilty to Federal Obscenity Charge

author: Andrew Buncombe
description: Disgraced former Democratic congressman Anthony Weiner is reportedly to plead guilty to a charge of sending obscene material to a minor, after federal authorities launched a “sexting” investigation.  The former political high-flyer and estranged husband of senior Hillary Clinton, Huma Abedin, is scheduled to appear in a New York court.
title: Anthony Weiner 'to plead guilty' after being accused of sexting a minor
